shift + enter --> "come in next line from middle of any line"
ctrl + F4 --> "delete existing tab"
alt + enter --> right click on 'attribute' >> show attribute's actions
ctrl + space --> show attributes
ctrl + d --> copy current line to the next line
ctrl + shift + F10 --> 'run' the code
shift + esc --> close terminal
shift + alt + up/down arrow key --> move lines up/down
click on file + space --> "show contents of file in preview"